before my mom gets home.

16:26.193 --> 16:28.070
Look, I thought we could both
benefit from the trip.

16:28.112 --> 16:29.947
That's what I'm trying to say.
Yeah, I see that.

16:29.989 --> 16:31.699
Me to bury my grandmother,
you to bone.

16:31.740 --> 16:33.409
(laughs)
Nice.

16:33.450 --> 16:37.121
Okay, when you put it like that,
it sounds terrible,

16:37.162 --> 16:38.998
but, like, come on, Lorri.

16:39.039 --> 16:41.166
Who knows if I'm gonna get
another chance to do something

16:41.208 --> 16:43.627
like this? It
times out perfectly.

16:43.669 --> 16:45.170
And he said
he got us a hotel room

16:45.212 --> 16:46.880
for when he gets off work.

16:46.922 --> 16:49.091
How old is this guy?

16:49.133 --> 16:51.719
He's 31.
Thirty-one?!

16:51.760 --> 16:54.054
Yeah.

16:54.096 --> 16:56.056
Does he know
how old you are?

16:56.098 --> 16:58.600
Nineteen...

16:58.642 --> 17:00.561
according to my profile.

17:00.602 --> 17:02.104
All right, I know
I'm not your mom,

17:02.146 --> 17:03.522
but this is not a good idea.

17:03.564 --> 17:05.941
It's a terrible idea.
I'm just saying.

17:05.983 --> 17:07.818
What-what happened
to all that,

17:07.860 --> 17:11.113
"Michael, why don't you do
what you want to do for once?"

17:11.155 --> 17:13.949
You remember that whole...
that whole interaction?

17:24.543 --> 17:26.503
Where are we?
Uh, we need gas.

17:26.545 --> 17:30.049
Okay, but I-I really am
kind of... kind of in a hurry.

17:30.090 --> 17:31.633
Oh, my God. Relax.

17:31.675 --> 17:33.343
Remember, I said
we have plenty of time?

17:33.385 --> 17:34.845
My phone says
we'll get there by 1:30.

17:34.887 --> 17:36.513
All right.

17:36.555 --> 17:39.099
Is there, like, a little store
here or something?

17:39.141 --> 17:42.019
'Cause I'm thirsty.
Uh, yeah, just to your right.

17:42.061 --> 17:45.272
Come on. Come on,
buddy. Come on.

17:45.314 --> 17:47.399
Come here.

17:58.160 --> 18:00.621
What are you
looking for?

18:00.662 --> 18:03.207
Uh, just some water.

18:03.248 --> 18:04.750
Oh.

18:04.792 --> 18:07.920
Here.

18:07.961 --> 18:10.047
