18:54.007 --> 18:56.093
(door bells jingle)

18:57.553 --> 18:59.179
Michael?

18:59.221 --> 19:01.723
Over here! Marco?

19:01.765 --> 19:03.475
Let's go.

19:16.864 --> 19:19.408
Are you good?

19:19.449 --> 19:21.285
Yeah.

19:22.369 --> 19:23.829
Guess what?

19:23.871 --> 19:25.622
What?

19:25.664 --> 19:27.875
I didn't just get gas.

19:27.916 --> 19:30.085
I got this.

19:32.546 --> 19:34.423
It's weed.

19:34.464 --> 19:36.216
Cool.

19:36.258 --> 19:38.093
Yeah, uh, th-there's a
dealer at that gas station.

19:38.135 --> 19:41.054
Everyone at school talks
about him, and, uh,

19:41.096 --> 19:44.266
well, I-I gave him 20 bucks
to roll me a joint. (chuckles)

19:44.308 --> 19:46.560
