you got ripped off.

19:46.602 --> 19:49.146
Uh, here, um, have some.

19:49.188 --> 19:51.940
No, I'm not smoking weed
right now, and neither are you.

19:51.982 --> 19:56.028
Why are you being all judge-y?
I just saw you buy vodka.

19:56.069 --> 19:58.197
First of all,
I'm over the age of 21.

19:58.238 --> 20:00.532
Okay, well, legal drinking age
here is 19, but whatever.

20:00.574 --> 20:02.409
Just-just focus on getting
to Thunder Bay, please.

20:02.451 --> 20:03.869
Getting to Thunder Bay

20:03.911 --> 20:05.412
and smoking weed
are not mutually exclusive.

20:07.664 --> 20:09.541
(coughing)

20:09.583 --> 20:12.044
Here, relax, have a puff.

20:12.085 --> 20:14.087
It's called a "hit."

20:14.129 --> 20:15.797
No.

20:15.839 --> 20:17.925
More for me.

20:19.676 --> 20:21.595
